From the Infowars web site ::

Alex welcomes back to the show former BBC researcher, journalist, and the man behind the website www. bilderberg.org, Tony Gosling. 

Alex also talks with Wayne Paul, the brother of Texas Congressman Ron Paul, about the economy and the state of the nation. In addition to working as a CPA, Wayne Paul has studied and focused on tax litigation and IRS negotiations. 

Alex also covers the latest breaking news on the economy and war.
